  "description": "std-calendar as a Function — owns the fetch + SELECT_DAY state machine; default bodyContent renders the month-grid + upcoming-events tree. `config.calendarLook` switches the body between the default month-grid ('month'), a day-grouped agenda list ('agenda-list'), and a 7-column week timeline ('week-timeline') while inheriting the same trait, state machine, emits, and listens.",
